Method Detail

generateHistoryArff

public java.util.ArrayList<ArffParkingObject> generateHistoryArff(ObservationPeriodicity periodicity)
this method creates history arff strings in the following way: 1) Looks for parking lots 2) Creates for each lots all the observations from db 3) checks the TIS webservice if new observations are available and persists them 4) Filters the observations if required (see ObservationPeriodicity) 5) creates for each parking place the arff string

Parameters:
periodicity - the time distance between ParkingObservation
Returns:
the list of ArffParkingObject, one for each parking place. If no objects are available, an empty list is returned
